data.description: Make this one your Home Sweet Home! One owner, concrete block home nestled in a culdesac and just minutes to I95 and US1. The home features extra insulation, a metal roof installed in 2018 and the air conditioner replaced in 2017. It's roomy with a formal living room as well as a family room. This is a split floor plan with a spacious ensuite. The back porch is screened and overlooks a roomy backyard with a shed and privacy fence.  Within an hour from Orlando airport, Disney and 30 minutes to the beaches. With interest rates are coming down, don't lose the opportunity to own this lovely home!
